                        }
                    ],
                    "keyframes":""
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "text": "We set off in July of 1905 as a determined group of farmers, iron workers and a couple of city boys.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "text": "We didn’t know then that we were on a journey from <em>obscurity</em> <strong>to immortality.</strong>",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "4",
                    "text": "As New Zealand’s first rugby team, The Originals, we spent 42 days at sea, riding the surging ocean’s currents to the UK. ",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "5",
                    "text": "Knowing the world assumed our fate already to be sealed, we created structured line-outs, something the world had never seen. ",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "6",
                    "text": "Still at sea, we sparked an innovative, and unpredictable style of play that would become our signature.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "7",
                    "text": "We discovered that with some clever rearrangement we could insert a pointed, attacking element into our backline. ",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "8",
                    "text": "And here, aboard the kauri decks of the Rimutaka, the First-Five eighths position was born.  ",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "9",
                    "text": "This was a bold move. A brazen challenge to the way things had always been. Defying the rules, the same way Steinlager does. Always has.",
                    "elements": [
                        {
                            "name": "",
                            "type": ""
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
